actions.message:
I'll guide you through the few things you need to fill out to be in our system.
Please start by going to <#435410989672955904> and reading through our rules.
When you've read the rules please go to the <#459854388207550492> channel, and fill out the following form. 
`!gear ap: aap: dp: accuracy: link:link.png class: level: trinaaxe:x/-` Please note that the trinaaxe should only have an x if you have it at tri, and your accuracy should be without Crystals. Also the amount needs to be after the : without a space so `ap:123`
After that you can use the `!gear` and then any of the values above to update it so `!gear level:xx` to update your level. You can also use the `.list` for see a list of everyones gear.


Now let me give you a quick rundown of our channels and commands
First we have <#435410609190993931> Here any important announcements will be posted.
Next <#435413979884421121> Here you need to post any absences you plan on taking from the game.
<#461120595451576320> Here any Node Wars or other kind of events will be posted, and you will be able to sign up by reacting to the message, please keep an eye on this channel.
<#435411235740057600> We will select random members to post a screenshot of their game before every node war. (No editing of the image, croping. And you need to have your gear, inventory with axe and other nodewar items and buff bar showing.)
That's it for important channels.
Then we have normal hang out channels, with bots ect, please note you can get my commands by using `.help` in any channel.

If you have any questions, please feel free to pm anyone in the leadership.
